Dialogue: 1,0:24:02.22,0:24:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让男子加快了步伐
Dialogue: 1,0:24:05.17,0:24:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,少年为了冲出瓶颈
Dialogue: 1,0:24:08.54,0:24:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,走向孤注一掷的赌局
Dialogue: 1,0:24:12.28,0:24:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 1,0:24:15.04,0:24:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 1,0:24:16.81,0:24:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,第21话 愚者的前进
Dialogue: 1,0:24:21.96,0:24:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗的导火索需要亲手点燃
